The Confederation of Icelandic Enterprise has 6 member associations. The member associations operate on the basis of the different industrial sectors and each of them has the initiative in company matters within its own sector. They are: &#xd;
&#xd;
Association of Financial Institutions in Iceland (SFF) &#xd;
Federation of district heatings, electric utilities, and waterworks in Iceland (Samorka) &#xd;
Federation of Trade and Services (SVTh)   &#xd;
The Federation of Icelandic Industries (SI)  &#xd;
Fisheries Iceland (SFS)  &#xd;
The Icelandic Travel Industry Association (SAF)
